channel.title: Interface help
channel.description:
the source i got only ahs the ancient magic interface... how do i set so if u switch to normal (alreayd made the switch code from a alter) you see normal magics, instead of anceints
Summery:
you click alter ancients on = yes normal magics off = yes change interface of magics to normal magics
you click alter ancients on = no normal magics off = no change interface of magics to anceint magics
you click alter change magics from ancients to normal
Thanks :)
